</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="127" pageNumber="836" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="127.[1482,2688,1752,2685]" pageId="127" pageNumber="836">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1482,1718,2259,2292]" pageId="127" pageNumber="836">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but Swynnerton’s Bush Squirrel is diurnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
